IN RE: Andrew T. ADAMS NO. 2018-B-1700 Supreme Court of Louisiana. October 29, 2018

ORDER

Considering the Joint Petition for Interim Suspension filed by respondent, Andrew T. Adams, and the Office of Disciplinary Counsel, IT IS ORDERED that Andrew T. Adams, Louisiana Bar Roll number 37388, be and he hereby is suspended from the practice of law on an interim basis pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 19.3, pending further orders of this court. Pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 26(E), this order is effective immediately.
